## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **DOAC 4-class 2010-2015** = warfarin 60+ year monopoly 종료. apixaban (Eliquis) 2012 + rivaroxaban (Xarelto) 2011 + dabigatran (Pradaxa) 2010 + edoxaban (Savaysa) 2015. INR monitoring 불필요 + 만성 stroke prevention paradigm shift. apixaban 가 2024+ 1L (lower bleeding).
2. **DOAC reversal 2015 + 2018** = idarucizumab (Praxbind) Fab fragment dabigatran 가역 + andexanet alfa (Andexxa) FXa decoy 가역. DOAC adoption 가속.
3. **factor XI inhibitor 2024** = next-gen 만성 anticoagulation paradigm shift — asundexian + abelacimab + osocimab + milvexian. 만성 thrombosis 없이 hemostasis 보존 hypothesis. asundexian OCEANIC-AF 2023 stroke 더 nominal — 임상 의미 변동. abelacimab AZALEA-TIMI 71 bleeding endpoint 충족.
4. **pulmonary vein isolation (PVI) 2024+** = 만성 catheter ablation rhythm control gold standard. AFFIRM/RACE rate vs rhythm equivalence 시대 종료, EAST-AFNET 4 + CABANA + CASTLE-AF 가 early rhythm control superior.
5. **pulse-field ablation (PFA) 2024** = FARAPULSE (Boston Scientific) + PulseSelect (Medtronic) FDA. non-thermal electroporation — 식도 + 횡격막 신경 + 폐정맥 협착 회피. RF + cryo ablation 후 paradigm shift.
6. **WATCHMAN + Amulet LAA closure 2015 + 2021** = 만성 anticoagulation 불내약성 환자 — LAA mechanical occlusion. PROTECT-AF + PREVAIL + Amulet IDE — non-inferiority warfarin.
7. **amiodarone 1985 vs dronedarone 2009** = amiodarone 폐 + 갑상선 + 간 toxicity 만성 — dronedarone iodine-free analog 가 less toxic but PALLAS permanent AFib 사망 증가 — paroxysmal/persistent 한정.
8. **vernakalant atrial-selective EU 응급** = Kv1.5 + Kir3 atrial-selective IV — Health Canada + EU 승인 but US FDA 미승인 (2008 사망 사건). atrial-selective concept 가 양자-VQE 의 fit.
9. **rate vs rhythm control paradigm** = AFFIRM 2002 equivalence → EAST-AFNET 4 2020 early rhythm control superior. 임상 paradigm 변동 — 양자-VQE 가 rate (β-blocker + CCB + digoxin) + rhythm (class IC + III) 모두 cover.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, AFib 임상 의미 한정. 만성 AFib + 만성 노인 + 만성 sleep apnea + 만성 K-AFib 임상 framework cross-link 만 가능.

